<p>That said, literally any tag you suggest would be fine.</p>
<p>I am also fine with using categories, though&#8230; I don't know whether or not that's adding too many layers of complexity.</p>
<p>EDIT: To be specific, a reason why this would be beneficial.</p>
<p>Note that we don't want any drafts to go live but with voting disabled, because then people might read&#8230; and then never come back to vote, potentially meaning early posters lose out on scads of votes. Unless there's a convincing case made otherwise, the gates will open for everyone at the same time that voting opens on Nov 22.</p>
<p>Doesn't mean we <em>can't</em> use categories though.</p>

